<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<!-- ============ HELP CENTER ============ -->
<style>
  .help-hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 20px 60px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
    position: relative;
  }
  .help-hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.10) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .help-hero .hero-icon {
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--accent, #00D8FF);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 0 18px rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.35));
  }
  .help-hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary, #f4f8ff);
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
  }
  .help-hero p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: rgba(244, 248, 255, 0.68);
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .help-container {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 20px 80px;
  }

  .help-glass-card {
    background: rgba(13, 20, 45, 0.72);
    backdrop-filter: blur(22px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(22px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.09);
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.38);
    padding: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    transition: all 0.30s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  }
  .help-glass-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.18);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45), 0 0 30px rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.04);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }
  .help-glass-card h2 {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.65rem;
    color: var(--text-primary, #f4f8ff);
    margin: 0 0 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }
  .help-glass-card h2 i {
    color: var(--accent, #00D8FF);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .help-glass-card p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    color: rgba(244, 248, 255, 0.68);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin: 0 0 16px;
  }
  .help-glass-card p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }

  /* FAQ Items */
  .help-faq-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 16px;
    padding-bottom: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
  }
  .help-faq-item:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  .help-faq-icon {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    min-width: 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.08);
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--accent, #00D8FF);
    margin-top: 2px;
    transition: all 0.30s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  }
  .help-faq-item:hover .help-faq-icon {
    background: rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.14);
    box-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.10);
  }
  .help-faq-content h3 {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-primary, #f4f8ff);
    margin: 0 0 8px;
  }
  .help-faq-content p {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.96rem;
    color: rgba(244, 248, 255, 0.62);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* CTA Button */
  .help-cta-text {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .help-cta-text h2 {
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .help-cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00D8FF, #0070F3);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 12px 32px;
    color: #050816;
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.30s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .help-cta-btn:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 216, 255, 0.30);
    color: #050816;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .help-glass-card { padding: 28px 20px; }
    .help-faq-item { gap: 12px; }
  }
</style>

<!-- Hero -->
<section class="help-hero">
  <div class="hero-icon">
    <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i>
  </div>
  <h1>Help Center</h1>
  <p>Find quick answers to your questions, troubleshoot common issues, and learn how to make the most of your Havenly experience.</p>
</section>

<!-- Main Content -->
<div class="help-container">

  <!-- Getting Started -->
  <div class="help-glass-card">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-rocket"></i> Getting Started</h2>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-plus"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>How do I create an account?</h3>
        <p>Creating your Havenly account is simple and takes less than a minute. Click the "Sign Up" button in the top navigation bar and choose to register with your email address, Google account, or Facebook profile. You'll receive a verification email — click the link inside to activate your account. Once verified, you can complete your profile by adding a photo, travel preferences, and payment information to unlock the full Havenly experience.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>How do I search for listings?</h3>
        <p>Use the search bar on the homepage to enter your desired destination, travel dates, and number of guests. You can refine results using our advanced filters — narrow by price range, property type (villa, apartment, cottage), amenities (pool, Wi-Fi, pet-friendly), and even specific features like ocean views or private chefs. Our AI-powered recommendation engine also suggests properties based on your browsing history and saved favorites.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>How do I book a property?</h3>
        <p>Once you've found a property you love, select your check-in and check-out dates, review the total price breakdown (including cleaning fees and service charges), and click "Reserve." Some properties offer instant booking, while others require host approval within 24 hours. After confirmation, you'll receive a detailed booking summary with check-in instructions, property access codes, and your host's contact information — all securely accessible from your Havenly dashboard.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>What payment methods are accepted?</h3>
        <p>Havenly accepts all major credit and debit cards (Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Discover), as well as digital wallets including Apple Pay, Google Pay, and PayPal. For bookings above ₹50,000, you can also opt for our interest-free installment plan, splitting your payment into 3 or 6 equal monthly installments. All transactions are protected by 256-bit SSL encryption and our Secure Payment Guarantee.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Booking & Payments -->
  <div class="help-glass-card">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-wallet"></i> Booking & Payments</h2>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-indian-rupee-sign"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>How does pricing work?</h3>
        <p>Each listing displays a nightly rate set by the property host. The total price you see at checkout includes the base nightly rate multiplied by the number of nights, plus a one-time cleaning fee (set by the host), and Havenly's service fee (typically 8–12% of the subtotal). Some properties may offer weekly or monthly discounts — these are automatically applied when your stay qualifies. You'll always see a full price breakdown before confirming your reservation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>Is a security deposit required?</h3>
        <p>Some hosts require a refundable security deposit to cover potential damages during your stay. The deposit amount is clearly displayed on the listing page and at checkout. Havenly does not charge the deposit upfront — instead, we place a temporary hold on your payment method. If no damage is reported within 48 hours of checkout, the hold is automatically released. In the rare event of a dispute, our Resolution Center team mediates to ensure a fair outcome for both parties.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-clock"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>How long does payment processing take?</h3>
        <p>Payments are processed securely at the time of booking. Your card is charged immediately for instant bookings, or upon host approval for request-based bookings. Host payouts are released 24 hours after guest check-in to ensure a smooth arrival experience. Refunds for cancellations are typically processed within 5–10 business days, depending on your bank or card issuer. You can track all payment statuses in real time from your account dashboard.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-invoice"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>Can I get invoices and receipts?</h3>
        <p>Absolutely. Havenly automatically generates a detailed receipt for every completed booking, accessible from your "Trips" section in your account. Each receipt includes a complete breakdown of charges, taxes, and fees. If you need a formal invoice for business travel or expense reporting, you can download a PDF invoice formatted with your name, booking reference, and GST details. Receipts are stored permanently in your account for easy access.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Account & Security -->
  <div class="help-glass-card">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-user-shield"></i> Account & Security</h2>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-key"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>How do I reset my password?</h3>
        <p>If you've forgotten your password, click "Log In" and then "Forgot Password." Enter the email address associated with your account, and we'll send a secure password reset link within minutes. The link expires after 30 minutes for security purposes. When creating your new password, we recommend using at least 12 characters with a mix of uppercase letters, numbers, and special characters. If you're still having trouble, reach out to our support team for manual verification.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>How do I enable two-factor authentication?</h3>
        <p>Two-factor authentication (2FA) adds a powerful layer of security to your Havenly account. Navigate to Settings → Security → Two-Factor Authentication and toggle it on. You can choose to receive verification codes via SMS to your registered phone number, or use an authenticator app like Google Authenticator or Authy for time-based one-time passwords (TOTP). We strongly recommend enabling 2FA, especially if your account contains saved payment methods.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-trash-can"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>Can I delete my account?</h3>
        <p>Yes, you can permanently delete your Havenly account at any time. Go to Settings → Account → Delete Account and follow the confirmation steps. Please note that account deletion is irreversible — all your booking history, reviews, saved properties, and personal data will be permanently removed from our systems within 30 days, in compliance with applicable data protection regulations. Active bookings must be cancelled or completed before deletion can proceed.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="help-faq-item">
      <div class="help-faq-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i></div>
      <div class="help-faq-content">
        <h3>How can I export my data?</h3>
        <p>Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and other privacy laws, you have the right to request a copy of all personal data Havenly holds about you. Navigate to Settings → Privacy → Export My Data, and we'll compile a comprehensive archive including your profile information, booking history, reviews, messages, and payment records. The export is prepared as a downloadable ZIP file and is typically ready within 24–48 hours. You'll receive an email notification when it's available.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <div class="help-glass-card help-cta-text">
    <h2><i class="fa-solid fa-headset"></i> Still Need Help?</h2>
    <p>Can't find the answer you're looking for? Our dedicated support team is available around the clock to assist you with any questions, concerns, or issues. Whether it's a booking problem, a technical glitch, or a general inquiry, we're just a click away.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="help-cta-btn">Contact Support</a>
  </div>

</div>
